<h2>Listing report — found item</h2>

<p><strong>Reporter:</strong> <%= @reporter_name %> &lt;<%= @reporter_email %>&gt;</p>

<p><strong>Found item:</strong> <%= @found_item.title %> (ID <%= @found_item.id %>)</p>
<p><%= link_to "View listing", found_item_url(@found_item) %></p>

<h3>What’s wrong / why they’re reporting it</h3>
<p><%= simple_format(@details) %></p>
